docs/V3_1_ROADMAP.md
docs/AGENT_DAEMON_CRITIQUE.md
docs/rfc/llm-provider-abstraction.md

# Relay server (AF-10) — a separate self-hostable deployable, not extension code
out/relay-server/**
src/relay-server/**
